Apply Backward node2vec on sink

{% raw %} 
from torch_geometric.utils import to_networkx
from directed_graphs.backwards import BackwardsNode2Vec
from torch_geometric.utils import to_networkx

G_nx = to_networkx(data, to_undirected=False)
node2vec2_model = BackwardsNode2Vec(G_nx, backward_prob=0.1, p=2, q=0.5, dimensions=50, walk_length=20, num_walks=800, workers=4)
emb = node2vec2_model.get_embeddings(window=20)
emb.shape
